# Code owners — require maintainer review on every change.
# GitHub auto-requests review from the owner(s) below when a PR touches
# matching paths. Combined with branch protection ("Require review from
# Code Owners"), this makes the maintainer the merge gatekeeper.
#
# !! REPLACE @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME with your actual GitHub handle. !!
# (CODEOWNERS needs a GitHub @username or team — an email won't work here.)

# Everything → the maintainer
*                       @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# Governance / licensing files — extra-protect (same owner; listed explicitly
# so they always require review even if you later add other owners above).
/LICENSE                @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
/CLA.md                 @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
/CONTRIBUTING.md        @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
/CODEOWNERS             @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
/.github/               @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
